---
title: Cajun BBQ Chicken Rice Bowl with Spinach, Cheese and Crispy Onions
description: Looking for a super quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Cajun BBQ Chicken Rice Bowl in just 15 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R07_W02_UK_UQ16878-3_Main_low-b53a8639.jpg
